{
  "stem": "14292.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- but the first time I slept under cover circumstances when the-- the second evening, somehow, an airplane dropped a bomb on-- the on the tent I was in.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "How that possible, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because in Germany, you know that it was no allowed those ones for lighting a cigarette.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was against the law during the evening hour.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But the camp was enlighted with search lights.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And-- so anyhow, I was in deep sleep.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My sputum was-- was dripping, because it was finally I could sleep well.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I awake, and people screaming, and dying, and obliterating.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I said, hell with it-- turned to other side and went to sleep.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I thought so it would be not a bad way to go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were absolutely doing nothing there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were just waiting to go even further.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so we had to go further.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was for us a temporary place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had to go to the place called Gunskirchen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Before we get there, we had to walk three days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now that time, I was about the same condition that most people were.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were bones and skeleton.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And someone who couldn't walk-- the Germans came, and they picked them up with a horse and buggy kind of arrangement.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then the people thought so that it was a very good thing to do.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And eventually, what happened with these people, they were on the-- went-- when we went to Gunskirchen, which was a death camp, they-- they were going to the open grave.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they were shot instant right there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They didn't have to go anywhere further That was the end of them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Then we had to go in a--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't escape.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The fire was probably stopped, and I was sleeping.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
